node.title: One dead after Mangakino crash
node.description: The single-car crash was reported at about 3.30am today.
node.content:
["One person has died following a single-car crash in Mangakino in the early hours of the morning.", "", "
\nPhoto: RNZ / Richard Tindiller\n
", "Police were alerted of the crash at about 3.30am today.", "A second person has been taken to Rotorua Hospital with serious injuries.", "State Highway 30 is now open after it was closed earlier to clear the scene."]
